    <item>
      <title></title>
      <link>https://wangcheer97.github.io/bio/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://wangcheer97.github.io/bio/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h2&gt;Welcome!&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&#xA;  This is Yuchen Wang (王雨晨). I am a first-year PhD student in the Urban &amp;amp; Regional Sciences PhD program at Texas A&amp;amp;M University (TAMU).&#xA;  Prior to this, I got my bachelor&#39;s and master&#39;s degrees in urban and rural planning at Huazhong University of Science and Technology (HUST).&#xA;  In addition, I am good at conducting interdisciplinary research on planning, geography and transportation.&#xA;  My current research interests are centered on &lt;span style=&#34;color: #002FA7;&#34;&gt;Smart Cities and Urban Informatics&lt;/span&gt;,&#xA;  specifically focusing on &lt;span style=&#34;color: #002FA7;&#34;&gt;Urban Digital Twins, Urban Foundation Models, GeoAI, AI for Planning, Urban Analytics, Climate-resilient Cities and Cybercrime&lt;/span&gt;.&#xA;  (Updated June 2026)&#xA;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
